P135 chess_piece_record () => R0[:32.0]
4[:32.0] => Z40.white.king.file[:32.0]
1[:32.0] => Z40.white.king.rank[:32.0]
(Z40.white.king.file[:32.0] * 10[:32.0] + Z40.white.king.rank[:32.0]) => R0[:32.0]
